title: Payout to Sidnexiv
body:
Payout to Sidnexiv for new Brand Caretaker role at .15eth per week, for provisional term of 35 days (5 7-day funding cycles) beginning once the payout is officially implemented. The provisional term gives a reasonable timeframe for Sidnexiv to contribute meaningfully, as well for the DAO to determine if a Brand Caretaker role is beneficial for the DAO ecosystem.

Responsibilities of this new role covers the following areas as they pertain to the Tiles brand:

1) contributions to brand building (guideline creation, creative ideation, outreach campaigns, community engagement)

2) In-house design services (physical products, social media assets, internal DAO assets)

3) Serving as a design resource for educational, accountability, and development purposes. 

## Proposal
If this proposal is approved, payout for Sidnexiv will be put in place for funding cycle 20. At the end of the provisional period at funding cycle 25, the DAO will vote again on whether the payout should be continued.
